text: Jussi Elo (6 January 1898 - 15 June 1957) was a Finnish diver. He competed in the men's plain high diving event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1898 births Category:1957 deaths Category:Finnish male divers Category:Olympic divers of Finland Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:People from Hämeenlinna
